{"tid":265562,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"見到啲人話工程爆煲就覺得好笑","createTime":"2017-05-31T17:07:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T17:07:18.000Z","uid":5866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"97131f7a9fea152bf8b0da9fe8ed34a224edc3a6","tid":265562,"uid":5866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T17:07:18.000Z","msg":"IT都話一直有新聞報導所以俾人長講<br />\n但咁耐以嚟話工程爆煲嘅都係零數據/資料佐證，全程得把口噏<br />\n舊登講爆煲講到嚟LIHKG<br />\n黑洞都爆到可以發光喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾時到工程業爆呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實班友係咪自己唔想進修/增值自己但又怕新人爭食，怕自己老闆知原來自己係個廢柴所以一直以嚟都瘋狂開post唧？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有行內巴打話重有請人/冇啲噉嘅事就無視人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫人唔好入行？收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}